Privacy Policy of Linked Squad

This Privacy Policy applies to all of our games, designed for all age categories, distributed by Linked Squad.

1. Collection and Use of Data

What data do we collect and why?

- Game data (e.g., game progress, unlocked characters, saved games) is stored both on the user's device and in the cloud. This allows us to restore data, assist users, and analyze gameplay. This data is anonymous and linked only to a specified identifier. It is not publicly disclosed or shared with third parties in individual form, but may be used in aggregated form for statistics (e.g., "most players reach a certain level") or in anonymous form.

We DO NOT collect the following personal information directly:

- Email address or other contact information
- Phone number
- Name and surname
- Exact locations/addresses
- Photos, videos, or recordings of users
- Files on the user's device not related to our products

Some third-party services may collect other personal information as stated in their privacy policies. Section 2 "Third-Party Services" lists these services and links to their privacy policies.

2. Third-Party Services

Our products use third-party services that may collect information about users. Below is a list of the services used, their purposes, and links to their privacy policies.

1. Advertising platforms:

- Unity Ads: [Unity Privacy Policy](https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy)
- IronSource: [IronSource Privacy Policy](https://www.is.com/privacy-policy/)
- Facebook Audience Network: [Facebook Privacy Policy](https://www.facebook.com/policy.php)
- AdMob: [AdMob Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
- AppLovin: [AppLovin Privacy Policy](https://www.applovin.com/privacy/)
- Yandex Advertising: [Yandex Privacy Policy](https://yandex.com/legal/confidential/)

2. Analytics services:

- Unity Analytics: [Unity Privacy Policy](https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy)
- Firebase Analytics: [Firebase Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)

If you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact us via email at LinkedSquad.help@gmail.com.